name: 李老师不是你老师
content: Recently, a Chinese woman was visiting the "Sky Capsule Train" attraction in Busan, South Korea, when she heard a Taiwanese tourist next to her say, "Hey? There are so many national flags on the train station, why is there no flag of the Republic of China?" The woman asked, "Taiwan doesn't belong to China, right?" After the Taiwanese tourist answered "yes", the woman scolded him, "You idiot, I'll take it away from you sooner or later!" https://pbs.twimg.com/ext_tw_video_thumb/1895516852727803905/pu/img/Uw6fzKCJbC2rCg8C.jpg
